screenshots show you too little.


149
00:09:39,306 --> 00:09:42,516
You can't actually understand
anything about the manner


150
00:09:42,926 --> 00:09:46,046
in which you're transitioning
from one screen to another


151
00:09:46,046 --> 00:09:47,436
if it's not moving at all.


152
00:09:48,446 --> 00:09:52,586
So we could go and build
a real working app.


153
00:09:53,716 --> 00:09:55,446
But apps actually
show you too much.


154
00:09:57,416 --> 00:09:59,086
There are a lot of
details involved


155
00:09:59,086 --> 00:10:02,366
