try built-in animations


162
00:10:25,956 --> 00:10:27,926
and compare those to
custom animations.


163
00:10:27,926 --> 00:10:30,606
Maybe we have some brilliant
new idea for an animation,


164
00:10:30,886 --> 00:10:32,146
