little experiments.


172
00:10:49,496 --> 00:10:51,356
We are trying things
out that aren't real.


173
00:10:52,256 --> 00:10:54,616
We are making these prototypes,
showing them to people,


174
00:10:55,276 --> 00:10:56,376
